      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是score等于threshold时触发。API会同步向Solana devnet发送交易，等待拿到signature后再返回给前端。最后前端要展示Solscan的链接让用户查看链上记录。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "score = threshold",
        "Solana devnet",
        "signature",
        "Solscan"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主干：用户完成使命后，前端调用POST /journeys/{id}/mint-badge，API向链上发交易，拿到签名后回传，最后前端展示成功状态和Solscan链接。",
      "elements_involved": [
