      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，但第一步的描述需要精确一点——应该是\"Complete mission (score = threshold)\"，这样和后面的mint-badge衔接更清楚。另外API返回给前端的不只是签名，还要包含explorerUrl。",
